<entry align="left">Relationship between frequency and period</entry>
<entry align="left"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>f</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mi>T</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></entry>
